OL,3,CNo and low-alcohol beer soaring in
OL,4,Cpopularity, pubs report
OL,6,FThe increasing range of options for
OL,7,Fdrinkers means the pub is "even more
OL,8,Finclusive and welcoming than ever
OL,9,Fbefore this festive season", the
OL,10,FBritish Beer and Pub Association
OL,11,F(BBPA) said.
OL,13,FThe trade association is calling on
OL,14,Fthe Government to align existing no
OL,15,Fand low thresholds with that of other
OL,16,Fcountries, to help drive sales and
OL,17,Fboost the economy.
