OL,3,CNo and low-alcohol beer soaring in
OL,4,Cpopularity, pubs report
OL,6,FIn the UK, the existing threshold for
OL,7,F"alcohol free" is 0.05% ABV (alcohol
OL,8,Fby volume), when it can be 0.5% ABV in
OL,9,Fother nations.
OL,11,FAligning the thresholds would provide
OL,12,Fa level of fairness for UK brewers,
OL,13,Fthe BBPA said.
OL,15,FBBPA chief executive Emma McClarkin
OL,16,Fsaid: "Whether someone is choosing
OL,17,Fmoderation, keeping pace with many
OL,18,FChristmas festivities, or just doesn't
OL,19,Fdrink alcohol, these sales show
OL,20,Fbrewers and pubs are catering to all.
