OL,3,CNo and low-alcohol beer soaring in
OL,4,Cpopularity, pubs report
OL,6,F"With the popularity of no and low
OL,7,Fincreasing, we stand ready to support
OL,8,Fthe Government in taking the necessary
OL,9,Fsteps to align our no and low-alcohol
OL,10,Fdescriptors with other markets.
OL,12,F"This important move would allow the
OL,13,Fcategory to continue to flourish,
OL,14,Fbenefit the consumer, and allow the
OL,15,Fpub to continue being a home away from
OL,16,Fhome."
