OL,3,CNo and low-alcohol beer soaring in
OL,4,Cpopularity, pubs report
OL,6,FLuke Boase, founder of non-alcoholic
OL,7,Fbrewer Lucky Saint, said: "There is an
OL,8,Fexciting opportunity for the
OL,9,FGovernment to support consumers in
OL,10,Funderstanding no and low drinks, and
OL,11,Fthat will create a hugely positive
OL,12,Fimpact on the health of the nation.
OL,14,F"Clear descriptors that align with
OL,15,Fother markets will help unlock
OL,16,Favailability, raise awareness and
OL,17,Fdrive consumption of alcohol-free
OL,18,Fdrinks across the country.
